  "texts": [
    "We present the STL-2DTCDN for long-term multivariate time series forecasting.",
    "It follows a hybrid structure similar to most recent studies but incorporates enhanced component methods.",
    "The STL-2DTCDN achieves the state-of-the-art performance on six practical multivariate time series datasets, with a significant improvement in prediction accuracy. 2.",
    "Different from canonical TCN designed for single time series, we present a 2-dimensional temporal convolution dense network (2DTCDN) for multivariate time series forecasting.",
    "The 2DTCDN, employing 2D convolutional kernels, casual convolution, dilated convolution, and a dense layer, making it highly effective at capturing complex interdependencies among various time series in multivariate time series. 3."
  ],
